# This directory holds ONLY generated EC2 benchmark output.
# It is intentionally empty in source control. Populate it by running the
# low-friction CDK + SSM harness (see docs/benchmarks.md):
#
#   scripts/build-stock-ami.sh
#   (cd infra/cdk && npm install && npx cdk deploy -c instanceType=c7i.metal-24xl)
#   scripts/ssm-bench.sh variant=saturate-iouring duration=30s
#
# The harness writes: report.md, rps.svg, throughput.svg, latency.svg,
# and matrix-saturate-iouring.csv into this directory.
